Actions.Text: REFERRED TO MENTAL HEALTH AND DEVELOPMENTAL DISABILITIES
COMMITTEE DISCHARGED AND COMMITTED TO FINANCE

Title: Enacts the New York commission for the deaf and hard of hearing act
Summary: Enacts the "New York commission for the deaf and hard of hearing act".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the executive law, in relation to enacting the "New York commission for the deaf and hard of hearing act"
